  User
  
 Troubleshooting
 ---------------
 - The ability to diagnose and resolve a problem;
1. Ask Questions
2. Isolating the Problem - root cause;
3. Follow the Cookie Crumbs - Figure out where the problem began and where it will end;
4. Start with the Quickest Step First;

Pitfalls
-----------
1. Don't go into autopilot;
2. Not finding the root cause;

Customer Service
-----------------
1. Show Empathy;
2. Be conscious of your tone;
3. Acknowledge the user;
4. Developing trust;

Documentation
--------------
- Ticketing Issues
- Tracking Issues - Bugzilla, JIRA, Redmine;

